{"tid":2215030,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"藏尾詩提「黑警3萬thx」被教局指專業失當 補習老師：只談惡有惡報非冒犯","createTime":"2020-09-23T16:28:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T17:03:19.000Z","uid":240362,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d2e7b7d664bedba49b7c0674f6434392d1d0c89a","tid":2215030,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T16:28:56.000Z","msg":"白色恐怖瀰漫教育界，教師於私人時間發表政治言論隨時被以言入罪，補習教師也未能倖免。有補習教師發表隱含「黑警死全家」字句的帖文後，遭教育局指專業失當。教育局重申，教師可有個人政治傾向，但發表意見時不應帶有仇恨。<br />\n<br />\n中文科補習教師文靜今年2月在私人社交賬戶發表帖文，內容指不解港人為何心腸狠毒、咒罵警察，並請年輕人發言前三思，然而串連每句的最尾一字，則成與文章意思相反的「黑警死全家 三萬thx!」。文靜憶述，當時因看到有中學副校長在私人帳戶發佈咒罵警員的藏頭詩引起軒然大波，她不解為何教育局及學校可干涉教育工作者的私生活，「私生活都要當成課堂咁去上一課？我覺得好瘋狂」，故她參考該副校的文章格式，撰寫類似文章。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/UFP37I5SSFDEDLQMO2NSGH3VPY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FUFP37I5SSFDEDLQMO2NSGH3VPY%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFN5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=7d449567\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FUFP37I5SSFDEDLQMO2NSGH3VPY%2F&h=d77060e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/UFP37I5SSFDEDLQMO2NSGH3VPY/</a>"},{"pid":"6352a1774e91fabae960843d19aa93adb374c51b","tid":2215030,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T16:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682a908ba7ecadaf15d9e5ae1ff7f88035b7e4c9","tid":2215030,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6352a1774e91fabae960843d19aa93adb374c51b","tid":2215030,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T16:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj